# Cache — <%= appName %>

Redis-backed cache service for <%= appName %>.

## Environment

```env
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379
CACHE_TTL_SECONDS=3600
```

## Usage

```typescript
import { cache } from './src/services/cache/index.js';

await cache.set('user:1', { id: 1, name: 'Ada' });
const user = await cache.get<{ id: number; name: string }>('user:1');
```

